Achievements.Name: Are You Not Entertained!?
Achievements.Description: Complete all 8 rounds of the Arena without taking a break

Achievements.Name: Hero, Their Health Is Low
Achievements.Description: Heal a follower on an Escort Quest. No, not *that* kind of 'escort'.

Achievements.Name: Combat, Evolved
Achievements.Description: Use an 'Ages of...' Potion with a combat multiplier of 20 or more

Achievements.Name: As Quiet As A Whisper
Achievements.Description: Defeat Whisper in a battle without losing any health.

Achievements.Name: For Every Choice, An Achievement
Achievements.Description: Become holier than Avo, or more evil than Skorm!

Achievements.Name: But You're A Wizard, Hero
Achievements.Description: Learn one of each spell type, or own one of each weapon type.

Achievements.Name: That's A Real Lunker!
Achievements.Description: Win 1st prize in the Fisherman's competition, or complete the boast for doing any quest naked.

Achievements.Name: Fight Cluck
Achievements.Description: Become the Fist Fighter's World Champion, or win the Chicken Hat in the Chicken Kicking Competition.

Achievements.Description: Pull the sword from the stone, or earn the top prize in the Archery Competition.

Achievements.Description: Donate a total of 100,000 Gold to the Temple of Avo, or sacrifice 10 people to the Chapel of Skorm.

Achievements.Name: Open Saysmemiddlefinger
Achievements.Description: Open all the Demon Doors, or show a closed Demon Door what you think of it.

Achievements.Name: Project Ego
Achievements.Description: Show all available witnesses a trophy in the trophy mini-game, or decorate your home with a trophy.

Achievements.Name: What Are Ya Sellin'?
Achievements.Description: Make a profit from selling to a trader, or steal an item using the "Steal" expression from a trader.

Achievements.Name: The Hero Of Time
Achievements.Description: Eat a Moonfish in Bowerstone during the day, or a Golden Carrot at night.

Achievements.Name: Beauty Or The Beast
Achievements.Description: Reach the maximum of your chosen attractiveness; ugly or beautiful!

Achievements.Name: Marital Relations
Achievements.Description: Receive a gift from your spouse, or flirt with an admirer in front of your spouse.

Achievements.Name: Ass Creed

Achievements.Name: There Is No Spoon
Achievements.Description: Use the power of mind control on an enemy, and have them kill one of their allies.

Achievements.Name: Out Of The Frying Pan...

Achievements.Name: The Ultimate Warrior
Achievements.Description: Treat yourself to a beard, haircut and tattoo, the 'ToupÃ©e And Tattoo Society' demands it.

Achievements.Name: That's My Man!
Achievements.Description: Level up a complete abilities tree, be it Strength, Skill or Will.

Achievements.Name: I Am Legendary
Achievements.Description: Earn enough Renown to be known in Albion as "Legendary".

Achievements.Name: See The Future
Achievements.Description: Connect Xbox SmartGlass to Fable Anniversary, isnâ€™t technology amazing!

Achievements.Description: Every tall Oak tree needed to have its acorn moment, this is yours.

Achievements.Name: The Graduation
Achievements.Description: Graduate from the Heroes Guild to become a real Hero.

Achievements.Name: Under A Full Moon
Achievements.Description: There's something going on in Knothole Glade under a full moon. ClichÃ©? Never.

Achievements.Description: Take on the might of everything that Albion has to offer. Well, almost everythingâ€¦

Achievements.Name: A Family Friend
Achievements.Description: Rescue the Archaeologist, and find the secret entrance into Bargate Prison.

Achievements.Name: Fishing In A Graveyard
Achievements.Description: Go fishing and digging in a graveyard, as if it's a completely normal thing to do.

Achievements.Name: (#SPOILERS)
Achievements.Description: It's time to defeat the super awesome boss, the one you will see if you unlock this achievement.
